        "Type": "usercreated",
        "Title": "Milk And Cookies",
        "Location": "LOCATION_ELEGANT_LLAMA",
        "PublicId": "131617298089",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/elegant/scene_llama.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 08428eba-b2f2-40f2-86c8-8157a8706426).Image",
        "Description": "Here at the Viñedo Yates, we take our Christmas traditions VERY seriously. Only the Yates family are permitted to change them, and that has not happened for over 60 years. When Don was informed that these three dared to try and change the traditions, he was infuriated. They wanted to replace the tried and true tradition of leaving cookies and milk out for Santa with leaving out wine and cheese, signifying the winery. Don has ordered us to eliminate them, but not harm any other staff.\rGood luck.",
